text: Poliaenus nuevoleonis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Chemsak and Linsley in 1975.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus nuevoleonis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Poliaenus nuevoleonis nuevoleonis Chemsak & Linsley, 1975 * Poliaenus nuevoleonis similnegundo Skiles, 1979 ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1975
